On Fri, Apr 2, 2010 at 6:46 PM, Pratt, Bob, VBABOST <bob.pratt(-at-)va.gov> wrote:

> I was always told 2nd gear was the best, but I can't remember why.

Think of the ratio of engine RPM to wheel RPM in the different gears.
First will push the engine too hard. It just needs a gentle nudge to
start.

